    <h1>Meet me, Yusoof</h1>
    <p class="indent-4">
      I stride through the crossroads of technology and nature , weaving code
      and crops into a harmonious tapestry. But it is the radiant light of
      Islamic teachings that ignites my journey, propelling me to share its
      brilliance.
    </p>
    <p class="indent-4">
      I am primarily proficient in modern web technologies and have expertise in
      devops tools. My motivation for becoming a software engineer was the time
      flexibility and financial stability it offered. In my spare time, I
      immerse myself in exploring emerging trends, often attending workshops and
      online courses to broaden my knowledge in the fast-paced world of
      technological advancement.
    </p>
    <p class="indent-4">
      I ventured into the world of agriculture. I run a farming business,
      specializing in planting edamame. This agricultural endeavor not only
      provides a source of income but also allows me to connect with nature and
      cultivate a sense of responsibility and stewardship for the environment.
    </p>
    <p class="indent-4">
      I am fascinated with Islamic culture above all of my doings, particularly
      the teachings based on the Quran, authentic Hadith, and the people among
      Ahl al-Sunnah wal-Jama`ah. I have a particular focus on Tawheed and
      Tafseer, the fundamental concepts of Islamic monotheism and interpretation
      of the Quran. My spiritual journey provides me with a sense of balance,
      purpose, and fulfillment. To further my spiritual commitment, I privately
      teach the Quran, sharing my knowledge and passion with those eager to
      learn. It allows me to deeply connect with my community and pass on the
      wisdom I cherish. By integrating spiritual concepts into my daily life, I
      navigate challenges with greater ease and approach situations with a sense
      of clarity and authenticity.
    </p>
    <p class="indent-4">
      In this era of virtual interconnectedness, I welcome all to engage and
      explore the convergence of technology and spirituality. You can connect
