        rel="noreferrer"
        target="_blank">GitHub</a
      >.
    </p>
    <p class="indent-4">
      Maa syaa Allah, tabarakallah. May our endeavors unfold as rich and diverse
      as the intricate tapestry weaving together my unique journey through life.
      This grace is from the bounty of our Lord. May Allah grant us all the
